# =============================================================================
#  Your life is private BY DEFAULT.
# =============================================================================
# This repo separates the FRAMEWORK (routers, docs, skills — tracked, updatable)
# from YOUR DATA (identity, people, decisions, memory — ignored, never published).
#
# The tracked template ships seed files named `*.example`. On first run,
# `tools/bootstrap.sh` copies each seed to its live filename — and those live files
# are ignored here, so your real content is never committed or pushed. Pull framework
# updates freely (see UPDATE.md); your data files are untouched.
#
# Result: you can make your fork public without leaking anything. No manual untracking.

# --- your live personal data (created from *.example seeds) ---
00_SELF/identity/character.md
00_SELF/identity/character_ai_mirror.md
00_SELF/decisions/decisions_log.md
00_SELF/decisions/feedback_patterns.md
00_SELF/people/people.md
00_SELF/memory/shared_memory.md
00_SELF/memory/todo.md
00_SELF/memory/SYNC_AXIS.md
00_SELF/memory/agent_brain/MEMORY.md
00_SELF/memory/agent_brain/USER.md

# --- your project memory (keep the registry + template, ignore the rest) ---
00_SELF/memory/projects/*.md
!00_SELF/memory/projects/INDEX.md
!00_SELF/memory/projects/_TEMPLATE.md

# --- memory archives + rolled backups ---
00_SELF/memory/archive/
00_SELF/memory/*.bak.*

# --- raw captured inputs (the `add` skill preserves these; they're private) ---
30_KNOWLEDGE/raw_inputs/

# --- personal life + the shared-agent ring (routers stay via the negations below) ---
50_LIFE/**
!50_LIFE/CLAUDE.md
90_SHARED/**
!90_SHARED/CLAUDE.md

# --- your actual projects/domains (their CLAUDE.md routers stay tracked) ---
10_WORK/**
!10_WORK/CLAUDE.md
!10_WORK/_PROJECT_TEMPLATE/**
20_DOMAINS/**
!20_DOMAINS/CLAUDE.md
!20_DOMAINS/_DOMAIN_TEMPLATE/**

# =============================================================================
#  Secrets — never commit
# =============================================================================
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.p12
*.key
credentials.json
*_token.json
*secret*
*.credentials

# conversation-memory store (if you place it inside the repo)
.conversation-memory/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# =============================================================================
#  OS / editor noise
# =============================================================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
node_modules/
.cache/
